{"type":"message","id":"2c0123bc","parentId":"52f40972","timestamp":"2026-03-11T12:11:04.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No memory results. This is a fresh workspace, so no prior context. I need to understand what the user wants. \"安装钉钉机器人\" means \"Install DingTalk robot\". \n\nDingTalk is a Chinese enterprise communication and collaboration platform. A DingTalk robot (机器人) typically refers to a bot that can be integrated with DingTalk to automate tasks, send notifications, etc. The user might want to:\n\n1. Set up a DingTalk chatbot/incoming webhook\n2. Install a specific software/bot on their system\n3. Configure a bot for OpenClaw to send notifications/commands\n\nGiven that this is OpenClaw and we're in a workspace, it's likely they want to integrate DingTalk with OpenClaw. But I need to clarify - I can't actually \"install\" DingTalk robot software on their system without understanding the specifics. \n\nI should ask for more details:\n- What kind of DingTalk robot do they want?\n- Are they looking for a chatbot that can interact with DingTalk groups/channels?\n- Do they want to receive OpenClaw notifications in DingTalk?\n- Or something else?\n\nI should provide guidance on what options are available and ask clarifying questions.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"I don't see any prior setup for DingTalk integration. To help you install a DingTalk robot, I need a bit more context:\n\n1. **Purpose**: What do you want the DingTalk robot to do? \n   - Send notifications (like alerts, status updates) to DingTalk?\n   - Receive commands/messages from DingTalk?\n   - Something else?\n\n2. **Environment**: \n   - Is this for a personal or corporate DingTalk account?\n   - Do you already have a DingTalk app/workspace where you can create a custom bot?\n\n3. **Integration type**:\n   - Do you want to use DingTalk's webhook API (incoming/outgoing)?\n   - Or are you looking for a pre-built bot framework?\n\nCommon approaches:\n- **DingTalk custom robot**: Create a bot in your DingTalk group/workspace → get a webhook URL → send HTTP POSTs\n- **DingTalk chatbot**: More advanced bot with conversational abilities\n- **Open-source projects**: e.g., `dingtalk-robot` or other frameworks\n\nWhat fits your needs? If you have a specific tool in mind, point me to its docs or GitHub and I'll help you set it up."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":12118,"output":799,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12917,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773231058056}}
