{"type":"message","id":"9da83663","parentId":"7ff2add4","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:18:45.330Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Example.com works. So the issue is that Bing and Baidu are blocking the request or returning errors. Possibly due to missing user-agent, but we added it. Still no output from Bing RSS. Could be that Bing requires cookies or something else. Or the RSS endpoint might not be accessible without a proper referrer.\n\nMaybe we can use a different service. Let's try the GNews API? That requires key.\n\nWhat about using a news aggregator like \"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=刘亦菲\"? That's Google News RSS. But Google News might also block. Let's try Google News RSS with -A and -L.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2e979c54372e43db8f941d14","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -L -A \"Mozilla/5.0\" \"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=刘亦菲\" | head -c 1000","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":25882,"output":356,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26238,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773235114664}}
