9%2580%25A0%25E5%259E%258B%25E6%25B5%25AA%25E6%25BC%25AB%2D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25BD%25A6%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259C%25BA%25E6%25AC%25A2%25E5%2591%25BC%2D%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%259C%25BA%25E6%2597%25B6%25E9%25A3%259E%25E5%2590%25BB%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%2Far%2DAA1XWR08&amp;rut=e39de291254594a6e0e6646f8ca8190f76e1000e7cecf2ad1847491606a5718e\">3月10日，巴黎时装周又现名场面——刘亦菲一身路易威登红色花瓣短裙亮相2026秋冬大秀，从下车瞬间到入场飞吻，直接引爆全球社交媒体。这波操作 ...</a>\n                      \n                    \n--\n            \n              \n                <div class=\"result results_links results_links_deep web-result \">\n                  <div class=\"links_main links_deep result__body\"> <!-- This is the visible part -->\n                    \n                      <h2 class=\"result__title\">\n                        <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"result__a\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.163.com%2Fdy%2Farticle%2FJGA8UD0Q05566SDO.html&amp;rut=b0c30cb06d012a586498c212a3c65e4c10a0bdad9a7cb03570518a14bba2ece3\">37岁刘亦菲突然高调宣布喜讯!恭喜啊，终于等到这一天了……|陈晓|韩星|宋承宪|娱乐圈_网易订阅</a>\n                      </h2>\n\n--\n\n                    \n                      <div class=\"result__extras\">\n                        <div class=\"result__extras__url\">\n                          <span class=\"result__icon\">\n                            <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.163.com%2Fdy%2Farticle%2FJGA8UD0Q05566SDO.html&amp;rut=b0c30cb06d012a586498c212a3c65e4c10a0bdad9a7cb03570518a14bba2ece3\">\n                              <img class=\"result__icon__img\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"\" src=\"//external-content.duckduckgo.com/ip3/www.163.com.ico\" name=\"i15\" />\n                            </a>\n                          </span>\n                          <a class=\"result__url\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.163.com%2Fdy%2Farticle%2FJGA8UD0Q05566SDO.html&amp;rut=b0c30cb06d012a586498c212a3c65e4c10a0bdad9a7cb03570518a14bba2ece3\">\n                            www.163.com/dy/article/JGA8UD0Q05566SDO.html\n                          </a>\n--\n                    \n                      \n                        <a class=\"result__snippet\" href=\"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.163.com%2Fdy%2Farticle%2FJGA8UD0Q05566SDO.html&amp;rut=b0c30cb06d012a586498c212a3c65e4c10a0bdad9a7cb03570518a14bba2ece3\">出道22年，刘亦菲公开的只有和宋承宪的一段长达2年的恋情。 分手后，宋承宪就很少在公众露面了，反观刘亦菲事业逐步上升，闯出了自己的一片天地。 就在11月5日这天，37岁的刘亦菲突然在深夜高调宣布喜讯。 粉丝们喜大普 ...</a>\n                      \n                    \n--\n            \n              \n                <div class=\"result results_links results_links_deep web-result \">\n                  <div class=\"links_main links_deep result__body\"> <!-- This is the visible part -->","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773235236840}}
{"type":"message","id":"34d6c2c5","parentId":"133f39f3","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:20:50.217Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! DuckDuckGo HTML is returning search results. The snippet shows:\n\n1. 标题: 刘亦菲近况大反转!隐退半年竟是搞大事，新身份让网友惊掉下巴\n   URL: news.qq.com/...\n   snippet: 消失半年，刘亦菲突然以宝格丽全球艺术大使的身份出现在巴黎时装周。\n   (This is about Liu Yifei appearing at Paris Fashion Week as Bulgari Global Art Ambassador)\n\n2. 标题: 刘亦菲亮相巴黎时装周造型浪漫，一下车便引全场欢呼\n   URL: www.msn.com/...\n   snippet: 3月10日，巴黎时装周又现名场面——刘亦菲一身路易威登红色花瓣短裙亮相2026秋冬大秀...\n   (About her appearance at Paris Fashion Week on March 10 in a LV dress)\n\n3. 标题: 37岁刘亦菲突然高调宣布喜讯!恭喜啊，终于等到这一天了……\n   URL: www.163.com/...\n   snippet: 出道22年... 11月5日这天，37岁的刘亦菲突然在深夜高调宣布喜讯...\n   (About her announcing some good news, possibly related to career or personal life)\n\nThis is good! We have some recent news. We need to extract more results and format them nicely.\n\nI should fetch all results and then present a summary.\n\nLet's pull all result blocks and extract title, URL, and snippet. The HTML structure appears: <div class=\"result results_links results_links_deep web-result \">, then inside, title in h2.result__title a.result__a, URL in a.result_url (but note the URLs are DDG redirect URLs, we need to decode? The actual URL is in the href after \"uddg=\" param. The snippet in a.result__snippet. But for our purpose, we can show the title, source (domain from the URL), snippet, and maybe date? There's no pubDate in these snippets. The news might have date inside snippet? Not always.\n\nWe can extract the source domain from the link: e.g., news.qq.com, www.msn.com, www.163.com.\n\nWe'll need to decode the URL from the DuckDuckGo redirect. The href looks like \"//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.qq.com%2Frain%2Fa%2F20251206A03OIC00&rut=...\" The actual URL is the value of uddg parameter (URL-encoded). We can decode it with `sed -e 's/.*uddg=\\([^&]*\\).*/\\1/'` and then `printf '%b' \"${//%/\\\\x}\"`? Or use `urldecode`. Simpler: we can just show the DuckDuckGo link? That would redirect to the actual news, but it's okay. Better to show the actual direct link. I can decode using `python -c \"import urllib.parse, sys; print(urllib.parse.unquote(sys.argv[1]))\"` but that's messy. I can skip decoding and just show the DDG link? The user might want the direct link. But we can also extract the visible URL from the a.result__url text: that shows \"news.qq.com/rain/a/20251206A03OIC00\" which is the direct domain path (but missing scheme). So we can combine: \"https://\" + that text.\n\nYes! There is a <a class=\"result__url\"> that displays the domain and path. That's perfect. The text content of that anchor is the visible URL, usually like \"news.qq.com/...\". So we can extract that.\n\nThus plan:\n\n- Fetch entire page.\n- Use awk or similar to extract each result block (separated by patterns). Could use grep -P with -o, but we can use a while loop reading lines and state machine.\n\nBetter: Use a proper HTML parser like `hxnormalize` and `hxselect` from html-xml-utils? Not installed. Could use `xmllint` with HTML parser? It might be installed. Let's check: `which xmllint`. In many systems it's there. Actually, earlier when we installed gh, it pulled many packages, but xmllint might be part of libxml2-utils. Not sure if installed. Let's check quickly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Let me check if xmllint is available:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d1fd46fb5585491496d5fb5c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which xmllint"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":33488,"output":1934,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35422,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773235236845}}
