{"type":"message","id":"7dd64af9","parentId":"d7cfec87","timestamp":"2026-03-12T02:50:41.463Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d4f1f3bc59bd40f4bb326db3","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\ngithub-memory-sync  GitHub Memory Sync\n  - 将 OpenClaw 的完整工作空间配置（SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md, USER.md, MEMORY.md, TOOLS.md, memory/*等）同步到 GitHub 进行备份和版本控制，支持跨服务器迁移。Use when user mentions GitHub backup, sync m...\n  - version: 1.1.0\ngithub-trending  Github Trending\n  - Fetch GitHub trending repositories by daily, weekly, or monthly periods with output in Markdown or JSON format.\n  - version: 1.0.0\ngithub-automation-pro  GitHub Automation Pro\n  - Automate GitHub tasks including advanced issue management, PR analysis, release creation with notes, repo stats, webhook triggers, and email support.\n  - version: 1.0.0\ngithub-ops  Github Ops\n  - GitHub 操作技能 - 创建仓库、推送代码、管理 Release。全自动，无需用户干预。\n  - version: 1.0.0\ngithub-chat-ops  GitHub Chat Assistant (Whatsapp)\n  - Manage a single GitHub repository via chat for non-technical requesters—after they share the repo URL and a temporary personal token, pull status, summarize who did what and when, and create/follow up on issues directly through the GitHub API.\n  - version: 1.0.0\ngithub-issue-reply-assistant  GitHub Issue Reply Assistant\n  - Free basic version that drafts a structured GitHub issue response and triage checklist. Reserves premium upgrade hooks for multilingual replies and fix-draft...\n  - version: 1.0.0\ngithub-issue-resolver  GitHub Issue Resolver\n  - Autonomous GitHub Issue Resolver Agent with guardrails. Use when the user wants to discover, analyze, and fix open issues in GitHub repositories. Triggers on...\n  - version: 1.0.0\ngithub-cli-tool  GitHub CLI\n  - Interact with GitHub using the `gh` CLI. Use `gh issue`, `gh pr`, `gh run`, and `gh api` for issues, PRs, CI runs, and advanced queries.\n  - version: 1.0.0\ngithub-actions-rerun