{"type":"message","id":"9d90bf19","parentId":"e7815039","timestamp":"2026-03-12T03:06:56.062Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The skillhub search doesn't seem to have found a Maplestory game. Let me try with different keywords like \"2d rpg\" or \"canvas game\" to find something that can be easily deployed.\n\nActually, let me think differently - the user asked to \"create a Maplestory game on github and deploy it\". This is a big task. I could:\n1. Search for existing open-source Maplestory clones or 2D RPG engines\n2. Create a simple one myself (using HTML5 Canvas or Phaser.js)\n3. Set up a GitHub Pages deployment\n\nBut first, let me search for existing projects that are ready to deploy.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"让我换用更通用的关键词搜索："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cf8eb3a578b64f4580cce0e0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"skillhub search 2d rpg game 2>&1 | head -n 50","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":87806,"output":345,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88151,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773284809381}}
