{"type":"message","id":"0d5c7768","parentId":"91ac4eb4","timestamp":"2026-03-12T03:07:13.803Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No direct RPG game found in SkillHub. I'll need to create a simple Maplestory-like game myself or use an existing open-source project. Given the constraints, I'll:\n\n1. Create a simple 2D RPG game using HTML5 Canvas/JavaScript (like a Maplestory clone)\n2. Push to GitHub\n3. Enable GitHub Pages for deployment\n\nLet me create a basic game structure with:\n- index.html (main page)\n- style.css\n- game.js (canvas-based game)\n- Readme\n- Use GitHub Pages to deploy\n\nI'll create a simple top-down 2D RPG with movement, enemies, items, and basic UI to resemble Maplestory's core gameplay.\n\nGame features:\n- WASD/Arrow keys to move\n- Click to attack\n- Enemy spawning\n- Item collection\n- Simple UI (health, level, gold)\n- Canvas-based rendering with tile maps\n\nI'll build this quickly and deploy.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"SkillHub 没有现成的“冒险岛游戏”技能。我们可以直接**自建一个简单的 2D RPG 游戏**并部署到 GitHub Pages。我来完成以下步骤：\n\n1. 创建仓库 `maplestory-2d`\n2. 用 HTML5 Canvas + JS 实现一个简易版冒险岛（移动、打怪、经验、金币）\n3. 提交并推送到 GitHub\n4. 启用 GitHub Pages 进行托管\n\n开始执行："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5fefd90145214a3f8a68dbcd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /tmp/maplestory-game && cd /tmp/maplestory-game && cat > index.html << 'EOF'\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <title>简易冒险岛 - 2D RPG</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"game-ui\">\n    <div class=\"status-bar\">\n      <span id=\"health-bar\">❤️ 100/100</span>\n      <span id=\"mana-bar\">💧 50/50</span>\n      <span id=\"exp-bar\">⭐ 等级 1 - 0/100</span>\n      <span id=\"gold-count\">💰 0</span>\n    </div>\n    <canvas id=\"gameCanvas\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\"></canvas>\n    <div class=\"controls\">\n      <p>操作：WASD / 方向键移动 | 点击攻击 | 拾取道具 ⌨️</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <script src=\"game.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\nEOF\ncat > style.css << 'EOF'\nbody {\n  margin: 0;\n  padding: 0;\n  background: #1a1a1a;\n  color: #fff;\n  font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: center;\n  align-items: center;\n  min-height: 100vh;\n}\n.game-ui {\n  text-align: center;\n}\n.status-bar {\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-around;\n  width: 800px;\n  font-size: 14px;\n}\ncanvas {\n  border: 2px solid #444;\n  background: #0f0f1a;\n}\n.controls { margin-top: 8px; color: #aaa; }\nEOF\ncat > game.js << 'EOF'\n// 简易冒险岛核心逻辑\nconst canvas = document.getElementById('gameCanvas');\nconst ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');\n\n// 玩家\nconst player = {\n  x: 400, y: 250, w: 32, h: 48,\n  speed: 3,\n  health: 100, maxHealth: 100,\n  mana: 50, maxMana: 50,\n  level: 1, exp: 0, expToNext: 100,\n  gold: 0,\n  frame: 0, dir: 'down', attacking: false, attackCooldown: 0,\n  color: '#4af'\n};\n\n// 状态\nconst keys = {};\nconst mobs = [];\nconst items = [];\nlet spawnTimer = 0;\n\n// 输入\nwindow.addEventListener('keydown', e => keys[e.code] = true);\nwindow.addEventListener('keyup', e => keys[e.code] = false);\ncanvas.addEventListener('mousedown', e => {\n  player.attacking = true;\n  player.attackCooldown = 15;\n});\n\n// 生成敌人\nfunction spawnMob() {\n  const side = Math.floor(Math.random()*4);\n  let x, y;\n  if (side === 0) { x = Math.random()*800; y = -30; }\n  else if (side === 1) { x = 830; y = Math.random()*500; }\n  else if (side === 2) { x = Math.random()*800; y = 530; }\n  else { x = -30; y = Math.random()*500; }\n  mobs.push({\n    x, y, w: 28, h: 28,\n    speed: 1 + Math.random()*0.8,\n    health: 30, maxHealth: 30,\n    color: '#f44',\n    flash: 0\n  });\n}\n\n// 生成道具\nfunction spawnItem(x, y) {\n  const types = ['gold', 'potion'];\n  const type = Math.random() > 0.7 ? 'potion' : 'gold';\n  items.push({\n    x: x + (Math.random()*30-15), y: y + (Math.random()*30-15),\n    type, w: 16, h: 16,\n    color: type==='gold'?'gold':'#0af'\n  });\n}\n\n// 更新玩家\nfunction updatePlayer() {\n  let dx=0, dy=0;\n  if (keys['KeyW']||keys['ArrowUp']) dy=-player.speed;\n  if (keys['KeyS']||keys['ArrowDown']) dy=player.speed;\n  if (keys['KeyA']||keys['ArrowLeft']) dx=-player.speed;\n  if (keys['KeyD']||keys['ArrowRight']) dx=player.speed;\n  player.x = Math.max(0, Math.min(800-player.w, player.x+dx));\n  player.y = Math.max(0, Math.min(500-player.h, player.y+dy));\n  if (player.attackCooldown>0) player.attackCooldown--;\n  else player.attacking = false;\n  player.frame++;\n}\n\n// 更新敌人\nfunction updateMobs() {\n  for (let i=mobs.length-1;i>=0;i--) {\n    const m = mobs[i];\n    const dx = player.x - m.x, dy = player.y - m.y;\n    const dist = Math.hypot(dx,dy);\n    if (dist < 30) { // 攻击判定\n      if (player.attacking && player.attackCooldown===1) {\n        m.health -= 10;\n        m.flash = 5;\n        player.mana = Math.max(0, player.mana-3);\n      }\n    }\n    // 移动向玩家\n    if (dist > 20) {\n      m.x += (dx/dist)*m.speed;\n      m.y += (dy/dist)*m.speed;\n    }\n    if (m.health <= 0) {\n      player.exp += 20;\n      player.gold += Math.floor(Math.random()*8)+2;\n      spawnItem(m.x, m.y);\n      mobs.splice(i,1);\n      // 升级\n      if (player.exp >= player.expToNext) {\n        player.level++;\n        player.exp -= player.expToNext;\n        player.expToNext = Math.floor(player.expToNext*1.2);\n        player.maxHealth += 20; player.health = player.maxHealth;\n        player.maxMana += 10; player.mana = player.maxMana;\n      }\n    }\n    if (m.flash>0) m.flash--;\n  }\n}\n\n// 更新道具拾取\nfunction updateItems() {\n  for (let i=items.length-1;i>=0;i--) {\n    const it = items[i];\n    if (player.x < it.x+it.w && player.x+player.w > it.x &&\n        player.y < it.y+it.h && player.y+player.h > it.y) {\n      if (it.type==='gold') player.gold += 5;\n      else if (it.type==='potion') { player.health = Math.min(player.maxHealth, player.health+30); player.mana = Math.min(player.maxMana, player.mana+20); }\n      items.splice(i,1);\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n// 绘制\nfunction draw() {\n  ctx.clearRect(0,0,800,500);\n  // 背景网格（地板）\n  ctx.strokeStyle = '#222';\n  for (let x=0;x<800;x+=40) { ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(x,0); ctx.lineTo(x,500); ctx.stroke(); }\n  for (let y=0;y<500;y+=40) { ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(0,y); ctx.lineTo(800,y); ctx.stroke(); }\n  // 道具\n  items.forEach(it => {\n    ctx.fillStyle = it.color;\n    ctx.fillRect(it.x, it.y, it.w, it.h);\n  });\n  // 敌人\n  mobs.forEach(m => {\n    ctx.fillStyle = m.flash ? '#fff' : m.color;\n    ctx.fillRect(m.x, m.y, m.w, m.h);\n    // 血条\n    ctx.fillStyle = '#333';\n    ctx.fillRect(m.x, m.y-8, m.w, 4);\n    ctx.fillStyle = '#0f0';\n    ctx.fillRect(m.x, m.y-8, m.w*(m.health/m.maxHealth), 4);\n  });\n  // 玩家\n  ctx.fillStyle = player.attacking ? '#fff' : player.color;\n  ctx.fillRect(player.x, player.y, player.w, player.h);\n  // 攻击范围（指示器）\n  if (player.attacking && player.attackCooldown>8) {\n    ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255,255,0,0.5)';\n    ctx.lineWidth = 2;\n    ctx.beginPath();\n    ctx.arc(player.x+player.w/2, player.y+player.h/2, 60, 0, Math.PI*2);\n    ctx.stroke();\n  }\n}\n\n// 主循环\nfunction loop() {\n  updatePlayer();\n  updateMobs();\n  updateItems();\n  draw();\n  // 敌人生成\n  spawnTimer++;\n  if (spawnTimer > 45 && mobs.length < 15) { spawnMob(); spawnTimer = 0; }\n  // 更新UI\n  document.getElementById('health-bar').textContent = `❤️ ${player.health}/${player.maxHealth}`;\n  document.getElementById('mana-bar').textContent = `💧 ${player.mana}/${player.maxMana}`;\n  document.getElementById('exp-bar').textContent = `⭐ 等级 ${player.level} - ${player.exp}/${player.expToNext}`;\n  document.getElementById('gold-count').textContent = `💰 ${player.gold}`;\n  requestAnimationFrame(loop);\n}\nloop();\nEOF","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":89123,"output":2728,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91851,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773284817386}}
