{"type":"message","id":"00dcf0a4","parentId":"eb393679","timestamp":"2026-03-12T03:07:50.547Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great! The repository is created at https://github.com/simplewei/maplestory-2d and code is pushed. Now I need to enable GitHub Pages for deployment.\n\nBy default, GitHub Pages uses the `gh-pages` branch or the `/docs` folder on the main branch, or the root of the main branch if configured. I'll set it to serve from the root of the main branch for simplicity.\n\nI can use the GitHub API or gh CLI to enable Pages. Let me check what's available.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"仓库已创建并推送：https://github.com/simplewei/maplestory-2d\n\n现在启用 **GitHub Pages** 进行网页部署："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5c2a3f6e8f6e4246be8bb414","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"gh api -X PUT repos/simplewei/maplestory-2d/pages --jq .html_url <<< '{\"source\":{\"branch\":\"main\",\"path\":\"/\"}}'","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":92574,"output":328,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92902,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773284863285}}
