{"type":"message","id":"609bab18","parentId":"e1f9f869","timestamp":"2026-03-12T03:08:03.106Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_dd1b0269b79d4c92b0b7ca09","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"切换到一个新分支 'gh-pages'\nremote: \nremote: Create a pull request for 'gh-pages' on GitHub by visiting:        \nremote:      https://github.com/simplewei/maplestory-2d/pull/new/gh-pages        \nremote: \nTo github.com:simplewei/maplestory-2d.git\n * [new branch]      gh-pages -> gh-pages\n切换到分支 'main'\n您的分支与上游分支 'origin/main' 一致。"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1204,"aggregated":"切换到一个新分支 'gh-pages'\nremote: \nremote: Create a pull request for 'gh-pages' on GitHub by visiting:        \nremote:      https://github.com/simplewei/maplestory-2d/pull/new/gh-pages        \nremote: \nTo github.com:simplewei/maplestory-2d.git\n * [new branch]      gh-pages -> gh-pages\n切换到分支 'main'\n您的分支与上游分支 'origin/main' 一致。","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773284883092}}
{"type":"message","id":"bbfadcc2","parentId":"609bab18","timestamp":"2026-03-12T03:08:08.965Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good! The gh-pages branch is pushed. GitHub Pages should automatically deploy from the gh-pages branch. But I need to verify if it's working. Let me check the URL https://simplewei.github.io/maplestory-2d/ - but that might not resolve until build is ready.\n\nAlternatively, the repo name is `maplestory-2d`, so the GitHub Pages URL will be:\nhttps://simplewei.github.io/maplestory-2d/\n\nI can check if the page is accessible with curl, but it might return 404 during build. I'll try.\n\nBut wait: GitHub Pages by default serves from the `gh-pages` branch automatically? Actually, for project sites, the default source is the `gh-pages` branch if it exists. So it should work after a minute.\n\nLet me test with curl to see if it's up.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"已推送 `gh-pages` 分支。GitHub Pages 通常会在几分钟内自动部署项目站点。\n\n**访问地址：**  \nhttps://simplewei.github.io/maplestory-2d/\n\n现在我来验证是否已发布："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c4569dfa243f4a789fe803cc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://simplewei.github.io/maplestory-2d/ | head -n 1","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":93695,"output":494,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94189,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773284883103}}
