{"type":"message","id":"258accf0","parentId":"0ce7fe72","timestamp":"2026-03-12T03:10:13.248Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good! I've successfully fixed the attack logic and pushed the change. The key fixes:\n\n1. **Attack cooldown logic**: Now when player clicks, if `attackCooldown <= 0` they can attack immediately, and `attackCooldown` is set to 20 frames\n2. **Single hit per attack**: Attack is triggered immediately on click (in the mouse event handler) and not during the update loop, preventing multiple hits in one click\n3. **Diagonal movement normalization**: Fixed diagonal speed by multiplying by 0.707 (1/√2) to maintain consistent speed\n4. **Attack range indicator**: The indicator now shows when cooldown > 15 (so lasting about 4-5 frames), better visual feedback\n\nThe game should now feel much more responsive. Let me inform the user about the fixes and that the code has been deployed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"已修复核心问题并推送更新：\n\n**修复内容：**\n- 攻击判定：点击时如果冷却结束立即造成伤害，并重置冷却为 20 帧\n- 防止重复攻击：攻击只在 mousedown 触发一次，而不是每帧判定\n- 攻击范围指示器调整\n- 斜向移动归一化，避免对角线过快\n- 代码结构清理\n\n部署地址：https://simplewei.github.io/maplestory-2d/\n\n请刷新页面测试。如果还有 bug（如穿墙、怪物无限生成、UI 不同步等），告诉我具体现象，我继续修复。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":95388,"output":516,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95904,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773285008067}}
{"type":"message","id":"f69ffbf3","parentId":"258accf0","timestamp":"2026-03-12T03:10:56.106Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-12 03:10 UTC] 继续优化"}],"timestamp":1773285056090}}
{"type":"message","id":"425554d6","parentId":"f69ffbf3","timestamp":"2026-03-12T03:11:18.550Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要对游戏进行更多优化，包括：\n1. 玩家动画和精灵图\n2. 改进攻击逻辑\n3. 增加更多游戏元素\n4. 修复已知bug\n5. 性能优化\n\n让我先看看当前的代码，然后进行迭代改进。主要改进方向：\n\n**游戏性改进：**\n- 添加玩家动画（站立、移动、攻击）\n- 改进攻击判定（方向性攻击）\n- 增加怪物类型（至少2种）\n- 添加音效（可选，使用Web Audio API）\n- 增加生命值、魔法值恢复机制\n- 优化UI显示\n- 添加开始/暂停功能\n\n**技术优化：**\n- 使用requestAnimationFrame更好地控制帧率\n- 减少不必要的重绘\n- 优化碰撞检测\n- 添加本地存储保存进度\n\n**部署优化：**\n- 添加PWA支持（manifest.json）\n- 优化移动端触摸控制\n\n我将先创建一个更完善的版本，然后推送。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"我来继续优化游戏，增加更多玩法元素和体验改进：\n\n**计划优化：**\n- 添加玩家朝向与角色动画（左右朝向下）\n- 攻击方向跟随鼠标/最后移动方向\n- 敌人AI优化（近战敌人）\n- 增加UI音效反馈（可选）\n- 添加开始/暂停界面\n- 增加更多道具类型（回复药水、金币袋、经验书）\n- 怪物波次生成（难度递增）\n\n开始实现："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_78d245a7d1cf49c6ae539041","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp/maplestory-game && cat > index.html << 'EOF'\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>简易冒险岛 - 2D RPG</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"game-ui\">\n    <div class=\"status-bar\">\n      <span id=\"health-bar\">❤️ 100/100</span>\n      <span id=\"mana-bar\">💧 50/50</span>\n      <span id=\"exp-bar\">⭐ Lv.1 0/100</span>\n      <span id=\"gold-count\">💰 0</span>\n      <span id=\"wave-count\">🌊 波次: 1</span>\n    </div>\n    <canvas id=\"gameCanvas\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\"></canvas>\n    <div class=\"controls\">\n      <p>操作：WASD/方向键移动 | 鼠标点击攻击 | 拾取道具 | 空格键暂停</p>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"pause-overlay\" class=\"overlay hidden\">\n      <h2>游戏暂停</h2>\n      <p>按空格键继续</p>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"start-overlay\" class=\"overlay\">\n      <h2>🎮 简易冒险岛</h2>\n      <p>消灭敌人，收集金币与道具，努力生存！</p>\n      <button id=\"start-btn\">开始游戏</button>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <script src=\"game.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\nEOF\ncat > style.css << 'EOF'\nbody {\n  margin: 0;\n  padding: 0;\n  background: #111;\n  color: #eee;\n  font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: center;\n  align-items: center;\n  min-height: 100vh;\n}\n.game-ui { position: relative; width: 800px; }\n.status-bar {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n  font-size: 16px;\n  padding: 0 4px;\n}\ncanvas {\n  border: 2px solid #555;\n  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);\n  image-rendering: pixelated;\n}\n.controls { margin-top: 8px; text-align: center; color: #aaa; font-size: 14px; }\n.overlay {\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;\n  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85);\n  color: #fff;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  justify-content: center;\n  align-items: center;\n  font-size: 24px;\n}\n.overlay.hidden { display: none; }\n.overlay button {\n  margin-top: 20px;\n  padding: 12px 30px;\n  font-size: 18px;\n  background: #4af;\n  border: none;\n  color: #fff;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n}\nEOF\ncat > game.js << 'EOF'\n// 简易冒险岛核心逻辑（优化版）\nconst canvas = document.getElementById('gameCanvas');\nconst ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');\n\nconst FPS = 60;\nconst TILE = 40;\n\n// 玩家\nconst player = {\n  x: 400, y: 250, w: 32, h: 48,\n  speed: 2.5,\n  health: 100, maxHealth: 100,\n  mana: 50, maxMana: 50,\n  level: 1, exp: 0, expToNext: 100,\n  gold: 0,\n  attackCooldown: 0, attackDuration: 10,\n  dir: 'right', attacking: false,\n  color: '#4af'\n};\n\n// 游戏状态\nconst state = {\n  paused: false,\n  started: false,\n  wave: 1,\n  mobsPerWave: 5,\n  spawnTimer: 0,\n  waveClear: false,\n  waveTimer: 0\n};\n\n// 输入\nconst keys = {};\nwindow.addEventListener('keydown', e => {\n  keys[e.code] = true;\n  if (e.code === 'Space') togglePause();\n});\nwindow.addEventListener('keyup', e => keys[e.code] = false);\ncanvas.addEventListener('mousedown', e => {\n  if (!state.started || state.paused) return;\n  if (player.attackCooldown <= 0) performAttack();\n});\n\n// 攻击逻辑\nfunction performAttack() {\n  player.attacking = true;\n  player.attackCooldown = 25;\n  let hitCount = 0;\n  mobs.forEach(m => {\n    const dx = player.x - m.x, dy = player.y - m.y;\n    const dist = Math.hypot(dx, dy);\n    if (dist < 70) {\n      m.health -= 12;\n      m.flash = 6;\n      player.mana = Math.max(0, player.mana - 2);\n      hitCount++;\n    }\n  });\n  // 命中反馈（可加音效）\n}\n\n// 敌人生成\nfunction spawnMob() {\n  const types = ['melee'];\n  const type = types[Math.floor(Math.random()*types.length)];\n  const side = Math.floor(Math.random()*4);\n  let x, y;\n  if (side === 0) { x = Math.random()*800; y = -30; }\n  else if (side === 1) { x = 830; y = Math.random()*500; }\n  else if (side === 2) { x = Math.random()*800; y = 530; }\n  else { x = -30; y = Math.random()*500; }\n  mobs.push({\n    x, y, w: 28, h: 28,\n    speed: 1.2 + (state.wave*0.1),\n    health: 30 + state.wave*5, maxHealth: 30 + state.wave*5,\n    color: '#f44', flash: 0,\n    type\n  });\n}\n\n// 生成道具\nfunction spawnItem(x, y) {\n  const roll = Math.random();\n  let type = 'gold';\n  if (roll > 0.9) type = 'potion';\n  else if (roll > 0.75) type = 'exp';\n  items.push({\n    x: x + (Math.random()*30-15), y: y + (Math.random()*30-15),\n    type, w: 14, h: 14,\n    color: type==='gold'?'gold': type==='potion'?'#0af':'#afa'\n  });\n}\n\n// 更新玩家\nfunction updatePlayer() {\n  let dx=0, dy=0;\n  if (keys['KeyW']||keys['ArrowUp']) { dy=-player.speed; player.dir='up'; }\n  if (keys['KeyS']||keys['ArrowDown']) { dy=player.speed; player.dir='down'; }\n  if (keys['KeyA']||keys['ArrowLeft']) { dx=-player.speed; player.dir='left'; }\n  if (keys['KeyD']||keys['ArrowRight']) { dx=player.speed; player.dir='right'; }\n  if (dx!==0 && dy!==0) { dx *= 0.707; dy *= 0.707; }\n  // 边界碰撞（简单矩形）\n  const nx = player.x + dx, ny = player.y + dy;\n  if (nx >= 0 && nx <= 800-player.w) player.x = nx;\n  if (ny >= 50 && ny <= 500-player.h) player.y = ny; // 留出顶部空间显示UI\n  if (player.attackCooldown>0) player.attackCooldown--;\n  else player.attacking = false;\n}\n\n// 更新敌人\nfunction updateMobs() {\n  for (let i=mobs.length-1;i>=0;i--) {\n    const m = mobs[i];\n    const dx = player.x - m.x, dy = player.y - m.y;\n    const dist = Math.hypot(dx,dy);\n    if (dist > 25) {\n      m.x += (dx/dist)*m.speed;\n      m.y += (dy/dist)*m.speed;\n    }\n    if (m.health <= 0) {\n      player.exp += 20;\n      player.gold += Math.floor(Math.random()*6)+1;\n      spawnItem(m.x, m.y);\n      mobs.splice(i,1);\n      checkLevelUp();\n    }\n    if (m.flash>0) m.flash--;\n  }\n}\n\n// 检查升级\nfunction checkLevelUp() {\n  if (player.exp >= player.expToNext) {\n    player.level++;\n    player.exp -= player.expToNext;\n    player.expToNext = Math.floor(player.expToNext*1.25);\n    player.maxHealth += 15; player.health = player.maxHealth;\n    player.maxMana += 8; player.mana = player.maxMana;\n  }\n}\n\n// 更新道具\nfunction updateItems() {\n  for (let i=items.length-1;i>=0;i--) {\n    const it = items[i];\n    if (player.x < it.x+it.w && player.x+player.w > it.x &&\n        player.y < it.y+it.h && player.y+player.h > it.y) {\n      if (it.type==='gold') player.gold += 3;\n      else if (it.type==='potion') { player.health = Math.min(player.maxHealth, player.health+40); player.mana = Math.min(player.maxMana, player.mana+25); }\n      else if (it.type==='exp') player.exp += 50;\n      items.splice(i,1);\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n// 波次管理\nfunction updateWave() {\n  if (state.waveClear && mobs.length === 0) {\n    state.waveTimer++;\n    if (state.waveTimer > 180) { // 3秒后下一波\n      state.wave++;\n      state.mobsPerWave = Math.floor(5 + state.wave*1.5);\n      state.waveClear = false;\n      state.spawnTimer = 0;\n    }\n  } else if (mobs.length < state.mobsPerWave && !state.waveClear) {\n    state.spawnTimer++;\n    if (state.spawnTimer > 40) { spawnMob(); state.spawnTimer = 0; }\n  }\n  if (state.waveClear) document.getElementById('wave-count').textContent = `🌊 波次: ${state.wave} (清空)`;\n  else document.getElementById('wave-count').textContent = `🌊 波次: ${state.wave} 剩余: ${state.mobsPerWave - mobs.length}/${state.mobsPerWave}`;\n  if (mobs.length === 0 && !state.waveClear) state.waveClear = true;\n}\n\n// 绘制\nfunction draw() {\n  ctx.clearRect(0,0,800,500);\n  // 地板网格\n  ctx.strokeStyle = '#222';\n  ctx.lineWidth = 1;\n  for (let x=0;x<800;x+=TILE) { ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(x,0); ctx.lineTo(x,500); ctx.stroke(); }\n  for (let y=0;y<500;y+=TILE) { ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(0,y); ctx.lineTo(800,y); ctx.stroke(); }\n  // 道具\n  items.forEach(it => {\n    ctx.fillStyle = it.color;\n    ctx.fillRect(it.x, it.y, it.w, it.h);\n    if (it.type==='gold') {\n      ctx.fillStyle = '#ff0';\n      ctx.fillRect(it.x+2, it.y+2, it.w-4, 4);\n    }\n  });\n  // 敌人\n  mobs.forEach(m => {\n    ctx.fillStyle = m.flash ? '#fff' : m.color;\n    ctx.fillRect(m.x, m.y, m.w, m.h);\n    // 血条\n    const hpPct = m.health / m.maxHealth;\n    ctx.fillStyle = '#333';\n    ctx.fillRect(m.x, m.y-8, m.w, 4);\n    ctx.fillStyle = hpPct>0.5?'#0f0':hpPct>0.25?'#ff0':'#f44';\n    ctx.fillRect(m.x, m.y-8, m.w*hpPct, 4);\n  });\n  // 玩家\n  ctx.fillStyle = player.attacking ? '#fff' : player.color;\n  ctx.fillRect(player.x, player.y, player.w, player.h);\n  // 攻击指示器\n  if (player.attacking && player.attackCooldown > 15) {\n    ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255,255,0,0.5)';\n    ctx.lineWidth = 2;\n    ctx.beginPath();\n    ctx.arc(player.x+player.w/2, player.y+player.h/2, 70, 0, Math.PI*2);\n    ctx.stroke();\n  }\n}\n\n// 主循环\nfunction loop() {\n  if (!state.paused && state.started) {\n    updatePlayer();\n    updateMobs();\n    updateItems();\n    updateWave();\n  }\n  draw();\n  updateUI();\n  requestAnimationFrame(loop);\n}\n\n// UI更新\nfunction updateUI() {\n  document.getElementById('health-bar').textContent = `❤️ ${Math.round(player.health)}/${player.maxHealth}`;\n  document.getElementById('mana-bar').textContent = `💧 ${Math.round(player.mana)}/${player.maxMana}`;\n  document.getElementById('exp-bar').textContent = `⭐ Lv.${player.level} ${player.exp}/${player.expToNext}`;\n  document.getElementById('gold-count').textContent = `💰 ${player.gold}`;\n}\n\n// 暂停切换\nfunction togglePause() {\n  if (!state.started) return;\n  state.paused = !state.paused;\n  document.getElementById('pause-overlay').classList.toggle('hidden', !state.paused);\n}\n\n// 开始游戏\ndocument.getElementById('start-btn').addEventListener('click', () => {\n  state.started = true;\n  state.paused = false;\n  document.getElementById('start-overlay').classList.add('hidden');\n});\n\n// 启动循环\nloop();\nEOF\ngit add -A && git commit -m \"Add wave system, new items, improved UI, and polished gameplay\" && git push origin main","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":95363,"output":3930,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99293,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773285056094}}
