{"type":"message","id":"cb4a7b7f","parentId":"be03a814","timestamp":"2026-03-12T03:18:54.558Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e7213ade676142898d180330","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\nnotebooklm-cli  notebooklm-cli\n  - Command-line interface to manage Google NotebookLM notebooks, sources, and generate audio, quizzes, reports, presentations, and visual study materials progra...\n  - version: 0.1.0\nnotebooklm-distiller  NotebookLM Distiller\n  - NotebookLM Distiller: Batch knowledge extraction from Google NotebookLM into Obsidian. Supports Q&A generation (15-20 deep questions), structured summaries,...\n  - version: 2.0.0\nnotebooklm-prompts  NotebookLM Prompts\n  - NotebookLM演示文稿提示词库，提供现代报纸、极简、漫画、时尚杂志、技术感、运动风等多种风格的幻灯片生成提示词。当用户需要生成演示PPT、幻灯片、Presentation deck时使用。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nnotebooklm-ppt  NotebookLM PPT\n  - 使用 NotebookLM CLI 生成 PPT 演示文稿。从预置风格模板库中选择模板，通过 notebook query 设置风格要求，再生成幻灯片。适用于需要快速将文档转换为演示文稿的场景。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nnotebooklm-ops  NotebookLM Ops\n  - Manage NotebookLM MCP auth lifecycle on Linux by automating GUI startup, auth refresh, status check, and cleanup for frequent cookie expiry.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nnotebooklm-cli-cookies  NotebookLM CLI Cookies\n  - Search and answer questions over documents already uploaded to NotebookLM using the nlm CLI. Use when users ask to find information, summarize sources, or query a specific NotebookLM notebook.\n  - version: 0.1.4\nnotebooklm-bypass  NotebookLM Auth Bypass\n  - Programmatic NotebookLM control with auto-recovery for authentication errors.\n  - version: 1.0.6\nnotebooklm-skill  Notebooklm\n  - Use this skill to query your Google NotebookLM notebooks directly from Claude Code for source-grounded, citation-backed answers from Gemini. Browser automation, library management, persistent auth. Drastically reduced hallucinations through document-only responses.\n  - version: 0.1.0\ntiangong-notebooklm-cli  NotebookLM CLI\n  - NotebookLM CLI wrapper via `node {baseDir}/scripts/notebooklm.mjs`. Use for auth, notebooks, chat, sources, notes, sharing, research, and artifact generation/download.\n  - version: 0.1.1\nnlm-notebooklm  NotebookLM Skill\n  - Expert guide for the NotebookLM CLI (`nlm`) and MCP server - interfaces for Google NotebookLM. Use this skill when users want to interact with NotebookLM pro...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nx-to-notebooklm  X To Notebooklm\n  - 将 X (Twitter) 文章解析并上传到 NotebookLM。使用 r.jina.ai 抓取内容，自动创建 Notebook 并上传文章。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nnlm  nlm\n  - NotebookLM CLI for listing notebooks, creating notebooks, adding sources, querying notebooks, generating studio artifacts, downloading outputs, sharing noteb...\n  - version: 0.1.0\nx-to-notebook  X To Notebook\n  - Push X/Twitter bookmarks into Google NotebookLM notebooks, auto-routed by bookmark folder. Use when the user wants to send bookmarks to NotebookLM, says \"pus...\n  - version: 1.1.0\nauto-ppt  Auto Ppt\n  - 自动生成精美 PPT 演示文稿 — 通过 Google NotebookLM 生成图文并茂、设计感十足的 AI 幻灯片，导出 PDF 到桌面。用户需自行登录 NotebookLM 网页版。标题微软雅黑 40 号加粗，排版震撼，逻辑图清晰，内容有深度有创新，引用权威数据。配合 desearch skill 使用效果...\n  - version: 0.1.1\ncontent-to-podcast  Content To Podcast\n  - Convert content from sources like YouTube, PDFs, and WeChat into podcasts, PPTs, mind maps, or quizzes with Google NotebookLM integration.\n  - version: 1.0.1\nhealth-data  Health Data\n  - Analyze Apple Health exports (export.zip or the exported folder) using xmlstarlet/jq to summarize activity, steps, sleep, and source counts. Trigger this ski...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nsolar-nexus  Solar Nexus\n  - Solar Nexus integration. Manage Organizations. Use when the user wants to interact with Solar Nexus data.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nbioinfo-daily-skill  Bioinfo Daily\n  - 每日生物信息学与肿瘤学研究进展日报生成器。使用 PubMed API 自动搜索前一天的 CNS 及 Nature Index 期刊文献，筛选生物信息学、肿瘤免疫、单细胞测序、空间转录组等领域的高影响力研究，生成包含中文亮点介绍的日报。使用场景：(1) 设置定时任务每天自动获取研究进展并发送到飞书 (2) 手动查询...\n  - version: 1.0.1\nzeelin-ai-detector  ZeeLin AI Detector\n  - 根据用户输入的文本，从语言风格和表达特征出发，估计其像 AI 生成的概率，并给出简要分析。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nyoutube-thumbnail-ai  Youtube Thumbnail Ai\n  - Automatically generate optimized YouTube thumbnails with AI using color theory, facial expressions, and typography to improve video click-through rates.\n  - version: 1.1.0"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1509,"aggregated":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\nnotebooklm-cli  notebooklm-cli\n  - Command-line interface to manage Google NotebookLM notebooks, sources, and generate audio, quizzes, reports, presentations, and visual study materials progra...\n  - version: 0.1.0\nnotebooklm-distiller  NotebookLM Distiller\n  - NotebookLM Distiller: Batch knowledge extraction from Google NotebookLM into Obsidian. Supports Q&A generation (15-20 deep questions), structured summaries,...\n  - version: 2.0.0\nnotebooklm-prompts  NotebookLM Prompts\n  - NotebookLM演示文稿提示词库，提供现代报纸、极简、漫画、时尚杂志、技术感、运动风等多种风格的幻灯片生成提示词。当用户需要生成演示PPT、幻灯片、Presentation deck时使用。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nnotebooklm-ppt  NotebookLM PPT\n  - 使用 NotebookLM CLI 生成 PPT 演示文稿。从预置风格模板库中选择模板，通过 notebook query 设置风格要求，再生成幻灯片。适用于需要快速将文档转换为演示文稿的场景。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nnotebooklm-ops  NotebookLM Ops\n  - Manage NotebookLM MCP auth lifecycle on Linux by automating GUI startup, auth refresh, status check, and cleanup for frequent cookie expiry.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nnotebooklm-cli-cookies  NotebookLM CLI Cookies\n  - Search and answer questions over documents already uploaded to NotebookLM using the nlm CLI. Use when users ask to find information, summarize sources, or query a specific NotebookLM notebook.\n  - version: 0.1.4\nnotebooklm-bypass  NotebookLM Auth Bypass\n  - Programmatic NotebookLM control with auto-recovery for authentication errors.\n  - version: 1.0.6\nnotebooklm-skill  Notebooklm\n  - Use this skill to query your Google NotebookLM notebooks directly from Claude Code for source-grounded, citation-backed answers from Gemini. Browser automation, library management, persistent auth. Drastically reduced hallucinations through document-only responses.\n  - version: 0.1.0\ntiangong-notebooklm-cli  NotebookLM CLI\n  - NotebookLM CLI wrapper via `node {baseDir}/scripts/notebooklm.mjs`. Use for auth, notebooks, chat, sources, notes, sharing, research, and artifact generation/download.\n  - version: 0.1.1\nnlm-notebooklm  NotebookLM Skill\n  - Expert guide for the NotebookLM CLI (`nlm`) and MCP server - interfaces for Google NotebookLM. Use this skill when users want to interact with NotebookLM pro...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nx-to-notebooklm  X To Notebooklm\n  - 将 X (Twitter) 文章解析并上传到 NotebookLM。使用 r.jina.ai 抓取内容，自动创建 Notebook 并上传文章。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nnlm  nlm\n  - NotebookLM CLI for listing notebooks, creating notebooks, adding sources, querying notebooks, generating studio artifacts, downloading outputs, sharing noteb...\n  - version: 0.1.0\nx-to-notebook  X To Notebook\n  - Push X/Twitter bookmarks into Google NotebookLM notebooks, auto-routed by bookmark folder. Use when the user wants to send bookmarks to NotebookLM, says \"pus...\n  - version: 1.1.0\nauto-ppt  Auto Ppt\n  - 自动生成精美 PPT 演示文稿 — 通过 Google NotebookLM 生成图文并茂、设计感十足的 AI 幻灯片，导出 PDF 到桌面。用户需自行登录 NotebookLM 网页版。标题微软雅黑 40 号加粗，排版震撼，逻辑图清晰，内容有深度有创新，引用权威数据。配合 desearch skill 使用效果...\n  - version: 0.1.1\ncontent-to-podcast  Content To Podcast\n  - Convert content from sources like YouTube, PDFs, and WeChat into podcasts, PPTs, mind maps, or quizzes with Google NotebookLM integration.\n  - version: 1.0.1\nhealth-data  Health Data\n  - Analyze Apple Health exports (export.zip or the exported folder) using xmlstarlet/jq to summarize activity, steps, sleep, and source counts. Trigger this ski...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nsolar-nexus  Solar Nexus\n  - Solar Nexus integration. Manage Organizations. Use when the user wants to interact with Solar Nexus data.\n  - version: 1.0.0\nbioinfo-daily-skill  Bioinfo Daily\n  - 每日生物信息学与肿瘤学研究进展日报生成器。使用 PubMed API 自动搜索前一天的 CNS 及 Nature Index 期刊文献，筛选生物信息学、肿瘤免疫、单细胞测序、空间转录组等领域的高影响力研究，生成包含中文亮点介绍的日报。使用场景：(1) 设置定时任务每天自动获取研究进展并发送到飞书 (2) 手动查询...\n  - version: 1.0.1\nzeelin-ai-detector  ZeeLin AI Detector\n  - 根据用户输入的文本，从语言风格和表达特征出发，估计其像 AI 生成的概率，并给出简要分析。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nyoutube-thumbnail-ai  Youtube Thumbnail Ai\n  - Automatically generate optimized YouTube thumbnails with AI using color theory, facial expressions, and typography to improve video click-through rates.\n  - version: 1.1.0","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773285534537}}
